				<wikidot:authorName>Subject90</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2905264</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Aside from it turning evil when the tag is off, this actually seems like an extremely useful item. You could make alloys with it easily without having to melt them down, if you have solid oxygen and hydrogen you could make ice, e.t.c. Or you can just use it as an extremely good murder weapon like the kids accidentally found out. No one would be able to figure out what happened.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
